    <body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_4606_p8">
                <lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>
		I beg to acknowledge the receipt of your<lb xml:id="p1-l10"/> letter of the <date when="1872-04-08">8<hi rend="sup">th</hi> </date> instant, in which you are<lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>
		good enough to ask us to make a<lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>
		practical trial of our system on the<lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>
		rocks of the <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">St. Gothard</placeName>. –
		</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_4606_p9">
                <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>
		The Machine Tunnelling Company is<lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>
		ready to send over at once a Machine,<lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>
		and, with reference to the offer of the<lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>
		Committee to bear a portion of the<lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>
		expense, I will leave the matter in<lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>
		your hands, feeling sure that full<lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>
		justice will be done us. –
		</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_4606_p10">
                <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>
		An Experiment with a single Drill<lb xml:id="p1-l22"/>
		would be useless, I presume, therefore,<lb xml:id="p1-l23"/>
		that the trial will be made on the<lb xml:id="p1-l24"/>
		line of the Tunnel itself, in which<note type="transcript">Kustode: case</note> <pb n="2"/>
                <lb xml:id="p2-l1"/>
		case, a short distance will have to be<lb xml:id="p2-l2"/>
		driven by hand, so as to enable the<lb xml:id="p2-l3"/>
		Machine to be fixed, and an<lb xml:id="p2-l4"/>
		emplacement will have to be formed<lb xml:id="p2-l5"/>
		on which to put the Boiler necessary<lb xml:id="p2-l6"/>
		to drive the Machinery.
		</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_4606_p11">
                <lb xml:id="p2-l7"/>
		We shall be happy to execute this<lb xml:id="p2-l8"/>
		preliminary work at cost price, and<lb xml:id="p2-l9"/>
		shall be glad to know whether you<lb xml:id="p2-l10"/>
		would wish us to do so, or if you<lb xml:id="p2-l11"/>
		will do it yourselves.?
		</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_4606_p12">
                <lb xml:id="p2-l12"/>
		The Machine that we should send<lb xml:id="p2-l13"/>
		would drive a Heading of the proper<lb xml:id="p2-l14"/>
		size for the Advanced Gallery, but<lb xml:id="p2-l15"/>
		the number of Drills would be increased<lb xml:id="p2-l16"/>
		when the machinery is made specially<lb xml:id="p2-l17"/>
		for the works of the <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">St. Gothard</placeName>. – and,<lb xml:id="p2-l18"/>
		of course, it will be impossible, until<lb xml:id="p2-l19"/>
		the men are accustomed to the<lb xml:id="p2-l20"/>
		work (and until we work with<lb xml:id="p2-l21"/>
		Compressed air) to obtain the<lb xml:id="p2-l22"/>
		speed that will be eventually<lb xml:id="p2-l23"/>
		reached –<pb n="3"/>
                <lb xml:id="p3-l1"/>
		for the trial, a Boiler sufficient to<lb xml:id="p3-l2"/>
		supply Steam to a Cylinder · 329 Metre<note type="transcript">sic! steht für 0.329 Meter</note> <lb xml:id="p3-l3"/>
		(or 13. inches) in diameter will be<lb xml:id="p3-l4"/>
		sufficient, and, although inconvenient,<lb xml:id="p3-l5"/>
		it will be quite easy to go a<lb xml:id="p3-l6"/>
		moderate distance with Steam. –
		</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_4606_p13">
                <lb xml:id="p3-l7"/>
		I shall be glad of your early reply<lb xml:id="p3-l8"/>
		as to our undertaking the preliminary<lb xml:id="p3-l9"/>
		work near <placeName type="place" key="Göschenen">Goeschenen</placeName>, If you wish<lb xml:id="p3-l10"/>
		us to do so, we should, immediately,<lb xml:id="p3-l11"/>
		send over an Agent, who would,<lb xml:id="p3-l12"/>
		shortly, be followed by the Machinery. –
		</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_4606_p14">
                <lb xml:id="p3-l13"/>
		In the event of our offer to<lb xml:id="p3-l14"/>
		contract for the whole of the Tunnel<lb xml:id="p3-l15"/>
		being accepted, I beg to assure<lb xml:id="p3-l16"/>
		you that we shall be prepared with<lb xml:id="p3-l17"/>
		any reasonable guarantee, for the<lb xml:id="p3-l18"/>
		fulfilment of our engagement, that<lb xml:id="p3-l19"/>
		may be required –
		</p>
    </body>
    <back>
